title: Total population of Amsterdam 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Number of inhabitants has rose over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Number of inhabitants, of value 862965.0 was reached at Year 2019
Minimum Number of inhabitants about 779808.0 was reached at Year 2011
